# _sys/boot scope 25 — path-based router (/stripe → stripe).
#
# Routes /stripe and /stripe/* to the stripe stack (verify a signed
# webhook, then call the Stripe API back to enrich it). See
# route-default.txcl for why this is EMIT, at scope 25, and guarded on
# `@route.to == ""`.
#
# @ is sugar for ._txc.
WHEN @route.to == "" && @src == "http" && @web.req.url.path =~ /^\/stripe(\/.*)?$/
  EMIT @route.tenant = "default",
       @route.stack = "stripe",
       @route.to = "stripe/0"
